@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_eprtvx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.22
    v2 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.44 * tmp + 0.45)) * wp.exp(v1))
    v2 = tmp
    v1 = wp.abs((v0 / wp.cos(v2 + 0.61)))
    data[tid] = v0
